{"tid":1347262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：元朗社區被挑撥「有反應是正常」　不會與白衣人割席","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:09:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e25fc30c049dd41e2f1e095f96dab5d64019c591","tid":1347262,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190722/s00001/e69e8740de33dc2f287d67539f951dfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2Fe69e8740de33dc2f287d67539f951dfc.jpg&h=6cc6c9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190722/s00001/e773d1acf2d469298aba4583dd2f25df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2Fe773d1acf2d469298aba4583dd2f25df.jpg&h=5bca13a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批白衣人士昨晚（21日）在元朗西鐵站襲擊市民和記者，有網上短片拍攝到建制派立法會議員何君堯與部分白衣人握手，其間何君堯獲白衣人讚揚是「英雄」。<br />\n<br />\n新界西立法會議員何君堯今日中午（22日）召開記者會，表示有人挑撥元朗社區，「有反應是正常的事」。他說自己並沒策劃暴力事件，而有片段顯示他讚揚白衣人，他解釋只是讚揚那些人「保家衛族」的精神，自己不會與他們「割席」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯表示，因為早前有網民聲言要於元朗進行光復行動，令元朗社區緊張，才有白衣行動。他又稱若有人刻意挑撥社區，「有反應是正常的事」。他其後表示支持當局依法辦事，不能以暴易暴。<br />\n<br />\n至於網上流傳何君堯昨晚與白衣人握手的片段，他表示自己與施暴者沒有任何關係，沒有策劃事件。他又稱，自己居於元朗，昨晚參加宴會送朋友回元朗，自己只是「啱啱好的時間在啱啱好的地方」。片段中可見何君堯向白衣人豎拇指，他表示，這是讚揚那些人「保家衛族」，並非讚揚他們打人。而片段中有白衣人讚他是英雄，何君堯稱，這因為自己「敢言」。<br />\n<br />\n有記者問何君堯會否與白衣人「割席」，他反問為何要割席，又稱任何人犯法都可以原諒。他續稱，保家沒有錯，但強調沒有要他們訴諸暴力。當記者質問何君堯為何與白衣人握手，他呼喝記者「坐低」、「要乖啲」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯今日凌晨（22日）在facebook個人專頁直播表示，早前有「黑衣人」在Telegram等網上社交媒體聲稱會走入元朗惹是生非，故元朗鄉紳居民有備而戰，「個個攞晒藤條」，更言「人哋嗰陣喺度，你走埋去係先撩者賤」。不過他強調，自己不認同任何暴力事件、以暴易暴。<br />\n<br />\n至於白衣人在西鐵打人是否與他有關，他是否主事者，何君堯稱「人哋發自本身的行動，不需要任何人教」，指出雖不應該有暴力行為，但帶有挑釁性的人不值同情。他又承認，昨晚有部分人他認識，有村長、教師等，反問為何他在元朗出現就「懶緊張」，但又不指摘泛民議員自6月以來未曾譴責暴力事件。<br />\n<br />\n他亦談及昨晚情況，說自己住元朗，昨晚飯後送朋友回元朗，經過見到穿白衣「保鄉衛族的衛士」，有人與他握手，表示支持他表態撐警恢復香港秩序。何君堯稱，知道一旦黑衣人出現，元朗鄉紳會做「保家衛族」工作，故昨晚到場是向相關人等提示法律問題，然後與他們合照。<br />\n<br />\n他又質疑有記者是滋事分子，稱要成立獨立調查委員會調查傳媒運作和制度，有否隨便讓人登記記者證「濫竽充數」。"},{"pid":"b3c190b19f1e4ec6ac571c21220120176ca80b4c","tid":1347262,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:44:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190722/s00001/1563755141298/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2F1563755141298%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=dd0ba7fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2F1563755141298%2F&h=8a355f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190722/s00001/1563755141298/</a>"},{"pid":"0b4b9f24ad9c058e78bee5e6855f1ca202d0b650","tid":1347262,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:46:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">殺，無赦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"486e163d083999501e8ec2b069f1526159c49a05","tid":1347262,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8fa138375141b3b9df674bede928f5deeb5e82","tid":1347262,"uid":231090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"撚有挑撥過你地"},{"pid":"6902bfa51f9521363c088368640cb9856432e0a0","tid":1347262,"uid":17873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街"},{"pid":"038373edb0ea11b64fb63c93b4f4542e74519f2b","tid":1347262,"uid":58958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"對住佢有反應都正常"},{"pid":"ebcfac3a73103be7d46c5575959f5e9e535d2031","tid":1347262,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"策劃恐怖襲擊係極嚴重罪行<br />\n<br />\n市民應可以101 拘捕權拘捕之 !<br />\n<br />\n有冇法律界講講 ?"},{"pid":"25d9e26df3dfcd4924a594e403ca73933db44b8c","tid":1347262,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"讀法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死人咩"},{"pid":"95787bcdee897036d7b215f09b5ea106d3bfd228","tid":1347262,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"上mtr打屯門人<br />\n叫保衛家園"},{"pid":"c3186c884dcdee8b6dca966e05adc314567c4720","tid":1347262,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"好阿，咁你地一齊落地獄啦"},{"pid":"c0664872920d61d70be8dab0d43854226ab5f438","tid":1347262,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"個個攞晒藤條唔行得過去?<br />\n<br />\n咁出街攞住吧刀唔係要比人拉，係要人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3e76f01ecf85a90b66ae9bc3d286fd206776b5","tid":1347262,"uid":281820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"即係有人講句說話嚇親你，你就可以打佢攻擊佢？何君堯唔記得咗香港係法治社會？<br />\n<br />\n合理化以暴力解決問題？<br />\n<br />\n個腦自己坐住咗？"},{"pid":"b4348f7bf7a6715d63d2e2cf437cb12667eb38fa","tid":1347262,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"何君妖挑撥我地喎 組隊打鳩佢係咪反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9033c04a1cb31c864a64da8335bd92d12bb3bc9b","tid":1347262,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043a153125e2cfef2d438fafff7876402374dc8a","tid":1347262,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"得罪大多數香港人.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1c4ab53e1673cd3902bec882c1b4748f6e3ac0","tid":1347262,"uid":33209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"好呀 千其唔好割呀"},{"pid":"abff8f3ada2a0b57afd46ea2c2c57cf7ecb2cbe3","tid":1347262,"uid":267548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:09:12.000Z","msg":"係呀，所以港共挑撥香港人，有反應是正常的事。"}]}